{"type":null,"faqId":33249,"title":"如何设置作为modem连接电脑","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">进入 设置-无线和网络-更多-移动网络共享-USB共享网络。选择“USB共享网络”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">安装好驱动后（驱动程序可以通过Hisuite安装），在PC侧，右键点击“我的电脑”，在弹出的菜单中选择“管理”，界面会显示新的网卡设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">备注：使用USB共享网络方式上网时必须打开数据连接，否则无法上网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">如果PC上有无线网卡等，可以用手机开启WLAN热点，PC通过WLAN连接到手机上网（目前支持Windows操作系统）。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7969","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748549000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"modem,连接,电脑","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}